node.text:
This spectacular 1.6 acre property rests high above the glistening waters of the Long Island Sound and Larchmont Harbor, with over 500 ft of private shoreline, a deep water dock, a jetty, and an area for swimming or launching a small watercraft. Magnificently sited on a lush promontory adjacent to Manor Park, this beautiful 8,182 SF, 1898 Victorian is designed to highlight the gorgeous panoramas from every room. Experience unobstructed views from the wraparound porch, bluestone patio, in-ground pool & spa. An original stable is now a 3 bed, 2 bath guest house with chic-retro kitchen. At the heart of this 3-level turreted icon is a great room that soars 2 stories with stairway to a glass cupola. Each space melds period grandeur with glamour. This home is unrivaled.
25 Park Avenue, Larchmont, NY $11,300,000
7 Bedrooms
6/2 Baths
Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own this extraordinary waterfront home, listed with @Mimi.Magarelli. Learn more via the link below.
https://wpsir.co/25ParkAvenue
 
 #JBFSIRListings #JBFSIRLarchmont #JBFSIRWestchesterCounty #BeyondTheCity #JBFSIR # SothebysRealty #WestchesterCounty

node.title: The crown jewel of Larchmont’s coastline

node.text:
Check out this incredible home for sale located in Carlsbad, California 📍 This Waterfront Compound offers 6 bedrooms, 8 bathrooms & 8,000 sqft of living space. Just completed in 2021, it is designed as an open floor plan with steel beam construction, allowing disappearing glass doors down the western portion of the living and dining areas. Located right off Tamarack overlooking the bay this home couldn’t be in a better location. Message me for more information!
#luxuryrealestate #luxuryhomes #carlsbad #realestate

node.text:
Check out this beautiful 5 bedrooms, 4 bathroom home available on Airbnb. “The Palm House” has everything you need, sleeps 12 people comfortably, huge pool in the back yard & just a 5 minute Uber to all bars and restaurants. Huge Thank you to @hildehomes for allowing me to stay here this week, click the link in @hildehomes bio to book your next stay. Another big shout out to @concishare for stocking the Airbnb with groceries, sending over a private chef & getting me to and from the airport. Give them both a follow! 
#luxuryrealestate #airbnb #luxuryhomes #scottsdale

A gated entry and stately brick exterior welcome you to this unparalleled west-facing estate on Hunts Point in Greater Seattle. Meticulously curated, sophisticated interiors open seamlessly to the infinity pool, terrace, and lawn to the shores of Lake Washington with Seattle skyline and Olympic Mountain views. Designed for entertaining, the 2016 home has timeless traditional lines with all the modern conveniences and amenities of luxury new construction, including an epicurean kitchen, a remarkable primary suite and exceptional style throughout. Impeccable. Exceptional. Rare. 

Offered at $28.5M USD. Please contact Tere & Moya at Team Foster (@teamfoster_re) of #Compass for more info. 🎥: @reesefilms

Welcome to Eagle’s Nest Estate on San Juan Island, WA. A world-class offering drawing in awe-inspiring views from Orcas, to Mt. Baker & the Cascades, to the San Juan & the international sailing channels. Bathed in light, interiors boast an unsurpassed commitment to craftsmanship and fine finishes. From the great room with soaring ceilings, to the epicurean kitchen, to the formal dining room for a party of fourteen, each space is perfectly curated. But it is the view and setting taking center stage. Mesmerizing, unforgettable, and must be seen to be believed. Crestron Smart Home system: control everything with your phone. Yes, perfection is acceptable. #EaglesNestEstate

node.text:
Listed by: @caribb.ian 🗝 
Impulse Beach Estate is 'the' high-end villa on Grace Bay Beach boasting 125 linear feet of white powder ecstasy merged with the ebb and flow of crystalline clear waters. Nirvana. This 'under roof' 21,000 square foot "hotel disguised as a home" luxury estate sits on Coconut Road in Turtle Cove Marina; a private canal boat dock sits to the south of the 1.3acres, offering ease of access to the best waters and beach(es) in the Caribbean and second best in the World for 2020 per Trip Advisor. The beautifully landscaped gardens comprise a private tennis court, private bar, and a Five Diamond Pool with cabanas and a secret changing room with a full bath. Accessed via a spiral staircase, the rooftop deck provides Tiki lights, a fire pit and lots of seating to set the stage for the perfect vantage point for sunsets and stargazing. There is no better entertainment spot anywhere on Island - bring your DJ. Impulse has an "upside down" floor plan that maximizes the views of Grace Bay.

Video Credit: @alexplorefpv Photo Credit: @tcvillas and @alexplorefpv

Exceptionally located on the oceanfront in a famed and treasured Laguna Beach neighborhood. A rare offering, this home has only traded ownership twice since its origin. A superior, unobstructed lot position allows for unmatched views in all directions. Dramatic, up close views of the crystal clear surf breaks, along with endless, forever views of Catalina Island, the California Coastline and horizon beyond. Day or Night, take in soothing ocean breezes that inspire and refresh the senses. Spacious outdoor terraces, decks that allow for amazing easy enjoyment of the world renowned Southern California weather, year-round. The intimate and comfortable interior atmosphere is richly enhanced by a palate of neutral colors in combination with extraordinary architecture. Each bedroom is ensuite and all offer spectacular, one-of-a-kind ocean views. The Master suite, of sumptuous proportions, enjoys breathtaking ocean views and an amazing full ocean view corridor Balcony. Perched and centrally positioned on a lightly traveled cul de sac, with a two car garage and two reserved driveway parking spaces. Don’t miss this rare opportunity to own an exceptional oceanfront estate in a prime Laguna Beach location.
• 4 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms
• 4,069 sqft of living space
• Listed for $9,888,000
Listed by: @celebrityrealtor_inc

Listed by: @devin__kay 🗝

A true one of a kind high floor AB Line combination at Two Park Grove boasting approximately 7,000 SF of living space curated by Deborah Wecselman & complimented by the highest quality finishes throughout. This private residence features 5 en suite bedrooms as well as 2 powder baths, extremely spacious living & entertainment areas, his & her Offices , 12 foot ceilings , Crestron system , & a 750+ bottle temperature controlled glass wine cellar. Custom Millwork, curated furnishings & finishes & floor to ceiling walls of glass showcasing 270 degree views are just some of the amazing features this home has to offer. From the moment you enter through your private elevator, the home seamlessly flows and provides a sense of elegance and warmth that any buyer would be lucky to call home. 

Enjoy 835 sf of outdoor space offering East, West and South exposures. Designed by OMA & Rem Koolhaas , Park Grove set a new Architectural standard in the quiet seaside enclave of Coconut Grove & offers an unrivaled lifestyle complete with world class amenities & dining. Residence 20AB comes with 3 assigned contiguous parking spaces as well as an oversized storage unit located on the same floor of the garage, all right next to the elevator. 

Offered Furnished, Price Upon Request

I wanted to personally Thank @jwmarriottnash for hosting me while I was in town. Nashville is such an incredible city.. if you love music, This is your scene! The JW has everything you need, Great location ($8 Uber or 10 minute walk to Broadway), Their lobby is beautiful, downstairs bar, rooftop steakhouse (Bourbon Steak) with 360° views of the city & huge swimming pool on the 4th floor. Stamford’s newest waterfront penthouse at Harbor Point is being offered for rent for the first time and brings luxury to new heights inside and out.
This stunning 4,455 SF custom-configured penthouse offers grand waterfront living. Enjoy floor-to-ceiling windows, incredible light throughout, and an open concept layout creating a grand space that’s perfect for entertaining. Living in luxury not only inside but outside, with 1,200 SF of private outdoor space spread through 2 private balconies and a private roof terrace with picturesque unobstructed panoramic views. Spread over three floors, Escape's penthouse is inspired by the streamlined elegance of the most sophisticated superyachts with countless features and resort-style amenities. This includes a state-of-the-art fitness center, pool, first-class screening room, climate-controlled wine tasting room, and a café to name a few. Move right in and call it home.
 
880 Pacific Street #PH S, Stamford, CT $35,000/mo
4 Bedrooms
4/2 Baths
Don’t miss out on the opportunity to rent this ultra-luxury waterfront penthouse, listed with @Stamford_Lifestyle_Real_Estate. Contact the listing agent for more information.

Set on 10+ park-like acres, the main house includes a 3-season screened-in porch and heated pool with a stone patio. The doors throughout the main floor open out to the wraparound deck, which overlooks the landscaped grounds and pool. Stroll the grounds through your own trails and enjoy seasonal views, stunning rock outcroppings, and over 2+ acres of beautiful fenced-in lawn.
